A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 State Lottery Fund – Laurel Race Course – Local Impact Aid
3 FOR the purpose of requiring the Comptroller, each fiscal year, to distribute from the State
4 Lottery Fund a certain amount of supplemental local impact aid to Anne Arundel
5 County, Howard County, and the City of Laurel from the proceeds of a certain lottery
6 game; and generally relating to the State Lottery Fund and supplemental local
7 impact aid for Anne Arundel County, Howard County, and the City of Laurel.
